== C-ARANB IF ~InParty("G#CASS")~ THEN ~[ARAN] Chatty Cassius. Mask's Left Hand, the skald never shuts up, eh? Hey, don't be lookin' at me like that, Haer'Dalis! I shut up. Occasionally. When th' wind is right.~
